HEADWORD: Ribwort
<hw>Rib"wort`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
species of plantain (<spn>Plantago lanceolata</spn>) with long, narrow,
ribbed leaves; -- called also <altname>rib grass</altname>,
<altname>ripple grass</altname>, <altname>ribwort
plantain</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

